   The National Weather Service's (NWS) Internet data
   source....Weather.GOV

   ....Bookmark address is: http://weather.gov

   Interactive Weather Information Network (IWIN) interfaces:
     * Animated Graphics version (High speed Internet connections)
     * Enhanced Graphics version (Mid Speed Internet connections)
     * Text version (Low speed internet connections)
     * National Weather Service Homepages
     * EMWIN links (Live computer data broadcasts via Satellite, Radio,
       Internet, more)

      Over One BILLION served since 1997

      Over 10,000 Web sites on the Internet link directly into this system.

